Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,击球手出局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.73,0:02:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我这种人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.14,0:02:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.64,0:02:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没礼貌
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.83,0:02:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 反正本来就想丢掉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说那对我已经没意义了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.23,0:02:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？打棒球不是需要球棒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没那个才能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.17,0:03:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.34,0:03:04.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是你累了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:08.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的 最好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.65,0:03:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要确认一下画面 请稍等
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样根本看不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.55,0:03:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.15,0:03:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“制作进行”是指管理时间表与工作人员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.05,0:03:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令现场工作能够顺利进行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担任这项工作如不能随机应变
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可就要被炒鱿鱼啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:04:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微睡的麻洛美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我说平沼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.03,0:04:03.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这根本行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.64,0:04:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今次新人又多 合不上拍子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.84,0:04:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离交货期还有两周吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“音响监督”是将音乐、效果音、声优等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切与声音相关的东西分类的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是会认识好多声优的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太“简朴”了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.59,0:04:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一话就这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.43,0:04:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.33,0:04:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五话以后自然会丰富起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“制作监制”是制作现场中最了不起的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作是筹集资金、 决定预算以及决定制作人员的工资
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有时还要处理一些麻烦事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之是会很辛苦的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.35,0:04:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在正一点点修改
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.12,0:04:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请宽容一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.46,0:04:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监督逃了也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这样根本没法录音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:02.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何也达不到效果
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能突然找其他人来做监督
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多作品 很难请人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于大型低气压的接近
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.25,0:05:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东京都中心部已发布大雨洪水警报
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交通受到大雨影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我是猿田
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.63,0:05:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在哪里啊 都7点了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在路上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开播只有30分钟了 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问题 交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在大厅等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.64,0:05:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 那一会儿见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界正期待着我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我掌握着命运
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.04,0:06:18.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 编剧住院了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.44,0:06:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 生病？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能写剧本吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.75,0:06:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正剧本总得改
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要脑袋没坏就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要手指能动 总会有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.83,0:06:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剧本还剩几本？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有10本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 手腕以上完全动不了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.84,0:06:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十只手指都是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.45,0:07:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 那请他保重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是逃掉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.43,0:07:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“摄影”的工作是把背景和赛璐珞画\N重叠而成的每一张画连续起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:19.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令其看上去像是动了起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对画面进行特殊效果和CG处理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.80,0:07:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是摄影的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是工作的最后一环
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.54,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最容易受进度延期影响的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.65,0:07:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我们会负责找代替者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.75,0:07:39.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“制作总监”是为了能按时完成作品
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掌握全部时间表 控制全话数的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.16,0:07:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总监如果不得力 时间表会乱得一塌糊涂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作现场将会变得非常凄惨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要赶上进程 肯定能找到人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我们的顶梁柱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.04,0:08:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但之前不是说找过的人全拒绝了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.65,0:08:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:15.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 我是M&F的鸠村
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来承蒙关照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.23,0:08:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们那里可辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为麻洛美的动画化忙死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过以月子为首的工作人员都很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.84,0:08:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次的作品也拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:41.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 今天我带来了麻洛美的新商品
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美抱枕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说动画界很多人都在工作室熬夜干活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我马上把她拿来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好疼爱她哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.84,0:09:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻洛美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我出了事谁负责
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.93,0:09:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是掌握着业界明天的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:51.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.84,0:10:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿田
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.84,0:10:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.64,0:10:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一句谢罪的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“演出”是各话的负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.75,0:10:22.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制动作的时机和场景的衔接
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把握整体的平衡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是制作中参与时间最长的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很容易蓄胡子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.23,0:10:34.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…也没有吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.23,0:10:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你不会道歉吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.23,0:10:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但把万能插口放在通道中间不合常理吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:48.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我为什么还停留在第250镜头吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.34,0:10:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你把那东西弄丢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.24,0:10:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是迁怒于人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.55,0:10:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请别这样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道别人在帮你收拾残局吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.75,0:11:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个呆子！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.93,0:11:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.23,0:11:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道睡 什么忙都帮不上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有空将自己的脑袋接上电吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.34,0:11:19.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在抵抗什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑瓜跟猴子差不多 自尊倒不输人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.14,0:11:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个猴子头！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.35,0:11:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是织田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.63,0:11:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 平沼先生出了事故？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.15,0:12:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.34,0:12:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(来自某匿名举报者)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.31,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(现在追踪的事故由“球棒少年”引起)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.95,0:12:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被“球棒少年”做掉的笨蛆虫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.62,0:12:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷可是不死之身！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.43,0:12:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(刚发生杀人案,怀疑是“球棒少年”所为)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.84,0:13:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.34,0:13:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经开播了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,替用的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.15,0:13:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,节目无法预期播映
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.66,0:13:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然承担不起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:13:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.24,0:14:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.06,0:14:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本大爷才不会犯那种错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说是被“球棒少年”打的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.54,0:14:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“演出”的鳄渊先生留下的空缺可难办了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.65,0:14:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“球棒少年”应该干掉几个没用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.06,0:15:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“色彩设计”负责设定人物小物品等的赛璐珞颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.26,0:15:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动画业界中当这工作的女性很少有
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.83,0:15:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要长得可爱一点 马上就会成偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.84,0:15:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 鳄渊负责的镜头怎样处置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.34,0:15:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部交给作监蟹江了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.94,0:15:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演出看过后能不能先给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.45,0:15:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等作监的话太花时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.35,0:15:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使不能一下子全拿来也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.75,0:15:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有作监检查好的稿？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张都没来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.04,0:15:44.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作监检查好的稿呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.34,0:15:48.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说想在家工作 明天会带来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不去回收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.95,0:15:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.75,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别找借口
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.65,0:15:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.95,0:15:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在期限内完成工作
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须像马车的马一样到处奔跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.96,0:16:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,净想享清福
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.22,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去回收
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到的话 就炒了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.93,0:16:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.83,0:16:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田那家伙装腔作势 当自己是谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.94,0:16:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.04,0:16:25.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄好了 弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜头…1、 2 、 3 、 4、 5
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.36,0:16:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作画监督 通称“作监”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.93,0:16:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通常动画由几位原画共同完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.93,0:16:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以画风不能统一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.83,0:16:48.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使其统一而进行修改就是“作监”的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.04,0:16:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面孔可是人物的生命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟹江小姐 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.84,0:16:58.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.75,0:17:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田那个混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都会以为那是在睡觉吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:11.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没笨到分不清人死活的地步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.23,0:17:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.33,0:17:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.05,0:17:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,熊仓先生 怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美术监督 通称“美监”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.06,0:17:45.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背景的负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以说是决定作品风格的重要一环
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.63,0:17:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.34,0:17:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不许碰 会留痕迹的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别被雨淋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.34,0:18:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.94,0:18:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 OK没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.85,0:18:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我走…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.42,0:08:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猿田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.63,0:18:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再说“你别干了”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死 给我去死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.43,0:18:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好难受…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.42,0:18:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.63,0:18:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(别来找我)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.55,0:19:21.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 我没听说过那种时间表
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:25.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但今天不完成就赶不上交货了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.63,0:19:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一目了然吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.53,0:19:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今天不完成的话就完了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.03,0:19:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你没法谈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把织田叫来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 今天不完成的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了 叫他来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.54,0:19:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请不要那样做
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.94,0:19:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,织田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.95,0:19:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚听说今天是最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是刚刚才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.23,0:20:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没说
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.73,0:20:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.63,0:21:11.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来只要把这个送到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.72,0:21:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 我是电视台的佐藤 怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.23,0:21:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑到最后的是本大爷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.84,0:21:52.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.84,0:21:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.64,0:21:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有才能
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.65,0:22:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.15,0:22:04.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是你累了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定是的 最好休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.36,0:22:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休息嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.90,0:24:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦告
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们到处流传谣言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.94,0:24:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金色靴子去的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走投无路的丧家犬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与狮子面面相觑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.75,0:24:20.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有入无回的迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.25,0:24:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立在故乡的招手犬
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.86,0:24:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救助还是欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.33,0:24:28.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.49,0:24:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁止入内
